Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: libc6-dev, libscanmem1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Library to locate and modify a variable in a running process
 Libscanmem provides the interfaces to scanmem and GameConqueror required to
